        "content": "### Pyroscope \u2014 Continuous Profiling\nFlame graphs in **Explore \u2192 pyroscope-monolith**. Profiles auto-collected from all pods by the alloy-profiles eBPF agent; server-side ingestion + query telemetry below.",
